snippet.title: Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets PS1 Walkthrough - Part 02
snippet.description:
==Heading to Hogwarts==
Ginny's gone missing so Harry needs to find her before he can go to Diagon Alley and subsequently return to Hogwarts. He and Ron then commandeer the car and fly to Hogwarts after missing the train and narrowly escape trouble.
